CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

October 13, 2010

[Cite as 10/13/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-4928.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2010-0425. [State ex rel.] Perez v. Edwards.

In Mandamus. On complaint in mandamus of Harry Perez. On S.Ct.Prac.R. 10.5 determination, cause dismissed.

Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
